一氧化碳中毒、缺氧致死。 坊間曾誤傳燒炭的方式能讓自殺者以較美觀的一面離世，但事實上由於燒炭自殺的直接死因是一氧化碳中毒，在人體缺氧的狀態下，自殺者遺體會加快腐敗與腫脹的程度，短時間內便會形成顯著膨脹。<br />\n<br />\n唔咁學術啦屌 你死前一刻係大量時間缺氧 然後先無意識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再者血液無氧係身體會發黑 你講紅 係岩岩死無耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n安樂死係好似訓左一教咁 打枝針ONLY<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係連登真係多無腦小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08cfc0d4e0f8c8e76351847bdd8c04290de73420","tid":991153,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc04736063725ee1f9232f54860d8713d2ca269b","tid":991153,"uid":22841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T07:17:03.000Z","msg":"一直想問一個問題 如果好似門徒咁 自制打一直重量既白粉針 係咪死得好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T07:39:58.000Z","msg":"自制難唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6099ef45e4715f99110768d430840181b37caf38","tid":991153,"uid":224646,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"19dd28dfce4665304cfd7535fa55312e6d659a48","tid":991153,"uid":133988,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2d6e2fc958473d85e6554324ede7b0cb67d7d9d8","tid":991153,"uid":224646,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ac52d9d146a92ccdca2c130b5957931ca157dce","tid":991153,"uid":133988,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T07:32:48.000Z","msg":"你係咪小學未畢業？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n燒炭死缺氧又何來安樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T07:36:52.000Z","msg":"燒炭死最安樂<br />\n暈左就冇感覺咁離開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n死左個樣都仲好靚仔面色紅潤<br />\n又唔洗客死異鄉<br />\n唔係做乜咁多人入長洲死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T07:39:54.000Z","msg":"你真係唔撚識咖喎<